23
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:39,980
But now

24
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,620
Tell me why I like him

25
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,500
Why? He is a serious nerd

26
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:46,940
So annoying. Why?

27
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,020
The most important thing is that

28
