64
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:12,340
Of course not. I will be with Baozi rather than him

65
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:18,140
People said, the more you hate someone, the more you want to do things you hate with him

66
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:20,420
Nonsense

67
00:05:21,180 --> 00:05:23,540
I just, just

68
