83
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:19,500
Don't worry. I'm ok

84
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:22,620
Ok, fighting

85
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:44,500
She doesn't have any sense of time

86
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:56,740
