I sing first

95
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:43,700
At this moment I suddenly have a sense of deja vu

96
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:50,620
Like yesterday, today, at the same time in screening

97
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:00,620
Almost

98
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,940
