99
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:12,700
At this moment I suddenly have a sense of deja vu

100
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:18,300
Like yesterday, today, at the same time in screening

101
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,140
Almost

102
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,100
You are too nervous

103
00:08:33,300 --> 00:08:35,260
Relax when you sing

104
00:08:35,860 --> 00:08:39,540
Relieve yourself if you want to sing it well

105
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:41,980
Relieve myself?

106
00:11:43,820 --> 00:11:48,860
Give it back to me

107
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:53,220
Give it back to me

108
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:55,620
Give it back to me

109
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:57,060
Give it back to me

110
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:07,020
Why would he even appear in my dream?

111
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,140
Yuan Lang

112
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:15,580
Yuan Lang, don't leave me

113
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:20,340
Lang, give it back to me

114
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:28,220
Give your heart back to me

115
00:12:30,540 --> 00:12:31,060
Heart

116
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:32,500
Heart

117
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:52,660
Yezi, do you know that there was paranormal event in our room?

118
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:54,620
It's real

119
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:56,140
Listen to me, it's real

120
00:12:56,700 --> 00:13:02,340
The cloth for cleaning windows was on my face this morning

121
00:13:03,060 --> 00:13:04,580
But I undoubtedly put it by the window yesterday

122
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:06,540
How weird

123
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:07,220
Yeah

124
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,620
I think you should visit the temple

125
00:13:08,780 --> 00:13:10,660
Maybe that's why I had no appetite yesterday

126
00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:13,140
Ok, time for class now

127
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,700
We can't finish our breakfast again

128
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,500
That professor's class

129
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,540
The bread

130
