145
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:06,400
You

146
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:10,020
Let's go

147
00:14:22,020 --> 00:14:23,260
Go, Zhuzi

148
00:14:23,500 --> 00:14:24,660
You are so cool today, you know

149
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:25,620
I think so

150
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:28,700
Fifteen thousand

151
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:30,300
I give you fifteen thousand

152
00:14:30,780 --> 00:14:31,820
If you stay away from Xiang Zeyi

153
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:34,700
So funny

154
00:14:34,860 --> 00:14:37,340
