166
00:15:29,980 --> 00:15:31,020
More than two thousand

167
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:33,100
Are you going to buy one?

168
00:15:34,900 --> 00:15:36,380
No, just curious

169
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:43,620
We need to hand in our work tomorrow

170
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:44,820
Are you ready for it?

171
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:48,340
I haven't seen you work because we aren't in the same class

172
00:15:48,980 --> 00:15:50,300
When will you show me your painting?

173
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:51,580
