180
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:07,540
Some careless people

181
00:16:08,540 --> 00:16:09,740
Here, here

182
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:17,220
The most important thing to the most important people

183
00:16:18,300 --> 00:16:18,820
Yeah

184
00:16:19,260 --> 00:16:19,900
Hurry, hurry

185
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:23,540
Let me have a look at your masterpiece

186
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:25,100
One two three

187
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,220
