194
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:54,820
No one would do it except her

195
00:16:58,660 --> 00:16:59,700
What to do now?

196
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,460
I will catch up on it by tomorrow

197
00:17:09,660 --> 00:17:11,020
How long did this painting cost?

198
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:12,300
Half of a month

199
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:13,420
You are crazy

200
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:14,900
