204
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:19,980
No, you can't

205
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:21,060
Leave me alone

206
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:24,140
You are so stubborn

207
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:03,380
So you want to run away?

208
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:05,940
What do you want? Put your hands off me

209
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:07,500
Get away

210
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:09,100
Ok, hands off

211
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:14,420
I'm here to tell you

212
00:18:15,540 --> 00:18:18,460
It was my mistake this afternoon

213
00:18:18,900 --> 00:18:20,100
My fault

214
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:22,060
I apologize to you

215
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:23,780
If you are angry

216
00:18:24,060 --> 00:18:25,220
