Then what?

227
00:18:57,780 --> 00:18:59,900
I'm warning you. Don't push me

228
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:02,900
Any proofs?

229
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:06,180
Now you wanna hit me?

230
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,300
Have you got any proofs?

231
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:12,860
I need to sleep now

232
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:14,900
I don't want to waste time with you

233
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,540
Bye bye

234
00:19:19,340 --> 00:19:21,060
Xu Wenjie, let's wait and see

235
00:19:21,180 --> 00:19:23,060
I will beat you someday

236
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:26,700
Why are you here?

237
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:29,380
I'm here to fight for the future painter

238
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:35,420
Let me have a look

239
00:20:42,380 --> 00:20:43,300
The future doctor

240
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,260
What are you doing?

241
00:20:45,780 --> 00:20:47,460
Don't pretend that you know painting

242
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:53,180
What's it underneath?

243
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:57,700
I soiled it incautiously

244
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:00,420
Even though I don't know painting

245
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:02,260
I know you haven't finished it

246
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,620
It's about 12 o'clock now

247
00:21:03,940 --> 00:21:05,700
If you fail to hand in your work tomorrow, even god couldn't help you

248
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,100
What?

249
00:21:14,140 --> 00:21:14,940
If god couldn't help you

250
00:21:15,340 --> 00:21:18,540
How about letting me help you out of the dilemma?

251
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:22,340
Ok, please help me

252
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:24,020
