266
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:41,540
I can't finish it with you like this

267
00:22:42,100 --> 00:22:42,600
Ok

268
00:22:42,860 --> 00:22:44,340
Just paint as I say

269
00:22:44,460 --> 00:22:45,580
I'm sure that you will get a good score tomorrow

270
00:22:45,860 --> 00:22:46,900
Ok

271
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:53,940
