294
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:18,740
Coming

295
00:24:31,300 --> 00:24:31,820
I

296
00:24:43,340 --> 00:24:44,420
What's going on?

297
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:45,540
Are you a thief?

298
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:59,060
She is a thief for stealing people's heart

299
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:00,580
What happened, Xirang?

300
00:25:00,740 --> 00:25:01,780
What do you mean?

301
00:25:03,340 --> 00:25:04,180
It's weird

302
00:25:05,340 --> 00:25:08,300
Something strange happens, if things get wrong

303
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:12,220
Leave it to me

304
00:25:13,700 --> 00:25:15,220
I will break off our relation if you open the door

305
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:19,620
Who said that I'm gonna open the door

306
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,340
You said that, Liu?

307
00:25:22,940 --> 00:25:24,700
Or Xixi said that

308
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:26,180
Look how cowardly you are

309
00:25:27,340 --> 00:25:28,860
Well, you can do it

310
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:33,500
It's your express delivery, ok?

311
00:25:34,740 --> 00:25:35,620
Such a manner

312
00:25:36,100 --> 00:25:37,580
Why no one answers the door?

313
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:39,860
Aunt Lee, I am gonna get it at once

314
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:40,900
Wait a second

315
00:25:43,420 --> 00:25:46,300
Yezi, can I go to get the express delivery?

316
00:26:01,780 --> 00:26:03,100
Aunt Lee, where is my parcel?

317
00:26:04,940 --> 00:26:06,300
You scare me. Why are you here?

318
00:26:06,460 --> 00:26:07,140
Why can't I be here?

319
00:26:07,300 --> 00:26:08,100
What are you gonna do?

320
00:26:11,060 --> 00:26:12,620
Aunt Lee, where is my parcel?

321
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:14,820
So big

322
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:17,140
Let me have a look

323
00:26:18,380 --> 00:26:18,880
What?

324
00:26:20,980 --> 00:26:21,580
Wait a minute

325
00:26:26,140 --> 00:26:26,980
Brother

326
00:26:29,100 --> 00:26:30,740
You are coming for Yezi

327
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:34,140
But failed, right?

328
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:36,300
She doesn't want to see you

329
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,340
I want to apologize to her

330
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:40,660
Apologize?

331
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:42,780
That incident

332
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:44,780
No wonder she is angry

333
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,540
She was bullied because of you

334
00:26:46,780 --> 00:26:47,660
So she feels bad now

335
00:26:50,300 --> 00:26:52,460
It's all my faults

336
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:57,540
Be an outright man please

337
00:26:57,660 --> 00:26:59,820
Wipe your ass first [It means deal with your staffs first]

338
00:27:00,220 --> 00:27:01,220
Before coming to Yezi

339
00:27:01,580 --> 00:27:04,580
Can you speak a little bit graciously, Zhuzi?

340
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:08,060
I want to make it straight

341
00:27:08,220 --> 00:27:09,180
Understand?

342
00:27:11,220 --> 00:27:13,460
Could you do me a favor?

343
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:14,500
What favor?

344
00:27:14,940 --> 00:27:16,420
Persuade her to meet me

345
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:17,700
I want to apologize to her by myself

346
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:21,140
We can't help you

347
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:22,620
She is very stubborn

348
00:27:22,940 --> 00:27:24,740
She won't take our advice

349
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:29,100
Then could you give me her phone number?

350
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:30,300
That's ok

351
00:27:31,980 --> 00:27:33,300
But any benefits?

352
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:34,060
What do you want?

353
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:34,980
Invite us to have a big meal

354
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:35,600
No problem

355
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:36,860
It's a deal. Give it to me

356
00:27:38,220 --> 00:27:39,940
Ok. You have got her phone number now

357
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:42,380
Remember, don't call her too late

358
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:43,300
She goes to bed very early

359
00:27:44,220 --> 00:27:45,020
Ok

360
00:27:45,500 --> 00:27:46,540
Bye, brother

361
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:47,300
Bye bye

362
00:27:51,460 --> 00:27:52,180
What an aid

363
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:54,020
Why have you bought something so heavy?

364
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:55,300
Some beautiful clothes

365
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,460
I can take it by myself

366
00:27:59,660 --> 00:28:00,160
Go

367
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:01,460
Just now

368
00:28:01,820 --> 00:28:03,100
You shouldn't reply so quickly

369
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:04,460
How should we tell Yezi?

370
00:28:04,980 --> 00:28:06,300
I'm helping her, ok?

371
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:07,780
No, you aren't

372
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:12,460
I'm relieving men and women in the world of worries

373
00:28:12,620 --> 00:28:14,060
She will thank me sooner or later

374
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:24,660
Yezi, how's your painting?

375
00:28:26,060 --> 00:28:27,460
Our teacher has put off the time

376
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:39,820
The eighteenth meeting of 130 Room begins

377
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:43,860
Where are the applauses? Where are the flowers?

378
00:28:48,780 --> 00:28:49,620
Perfect. Here is a flower

379
00:28:50,740 --> 00:28:53,740
The theme of our meeting tonight is

380
00:28:54,260 --> 00:28:56,700
What does your favorite people look like?

381
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:58,500
Start from you

382
00:28:59,620 --> 00:29:00,260
Ok

383
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:03,220
Of course I like Yuan Lang best

384
00:29:06,620 --> 00:29:07,420
Your turn now

385
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:11,940
Who do you like best, Xixi?

386
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:13,780
No need to ask her

387
00:29:14,180 --> 00:29:14,940
Xixi

388
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:16,780
Likes Haha without doubt [Xixi and Haha both mean laughter in Chinese]

389
00:29:20,900 --> 00:29:21,940
Liu Xirang, shut up

390
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:25,180
What about your favorite people?

391
00:29:25,340 --> 00:29:26,420
I like Jay Chou best [A singer's name]

392
00:29:26,980 --> 00:29:27,980
You have driven me mad

393
00:29:32,300 --> 00:29:34,860
Actually I kind of like Xiang Zeyi

394
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:38,300
But he doesn't like me

395
00:29:40,420 --> 00:29:41,900
Because you are ugly

396
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:42,580
What?

397
00:29:42,980 --> 00:29:43,540
Too ugly

398
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:45,260
I want to

399
00:29:46,900 --> 00:29:48,140
What? Give me a banana?

400
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,500
Of course not

401
00:29:50,700 --> 00:29:52,540
[If you are not angry anymore, come to me in the classroom tomorrow. We can continue to practice the song. From Xiang Zeyi]

402
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:00,940
Let's wait and see

403
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:01,860
What would you do?

404
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:04,500
What are you doing?

405
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:05,940
Playing the piano?

406
00:30:10,460 --> 00:30:11,900
Dare you say it again?

407
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:15,180
Dare you say it again, Liu Xirang?

408
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:17,540
You are ugly

409
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,860
Who do you mean?

410
00:30:19,220 --> 00:30:19,940
You

411
00:30:20,100 --> 00:30:21,140
It's you that are ugly

412
00:30:21,340 --> 00:30:23,260
You are ugly, flat-chest

413
00:30:24,180 --> 00:30:25,300
All of you are ugly

414
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:26,380
Come here

415
00:30:26,820 --> 00:30:27,740
I don't believe it

416
00:31:40,820 --> 00:31:41,380
Yes?

417
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:44,380
Has she fallen asleep?

418
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:47,460
Yes, she has. Don't worry

419
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:49,420
Thank you

420
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:51,140
Never mind

421
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:54,180
I owe you a treat

422
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:55,620
Ok

423
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:02,860
Zhuzi is firm in speech but soft in heart

424
00:32:03,860 --> 00:32:05,500
She cares about you very much

425
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:08,340
Do you know that she has changed a lot for you?

426
00:32:08,820 --> 00:32:09,460
I know

427
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:11,820
We will be good

428
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,180
Good night

429
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:35,020
I think I still hate him

430
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:41,620
But I can't give up hating him now

431
00:33:02,740 --> 00:33:03,500
Xiang Zeyi

432
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:05,660
It's a national competition

433
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:08,780
It will be good for you to compete in it

434
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:09,900
Professor Wu

435
00:33:10,420 --> 00:33:12,500
You want me to compete in it, right?

436
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:17,420
But I need you to promise me one thing

437
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,460
What is it?

438
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:20,700
It's easy

439
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:25,820
Put off a few days for freshmen in Faculty of Chinese Painting to prepare their work

440
00:33:28,740 --> 00:33:32,140
Why does it matter you whether they hand in their work or not?

441
00:33:34,340 --> 00:33:35,620
Just promise me

442
00:33:36,820 --> 00:33:41,780
I will compete in the Anime Contest and make our school proud

443
00:33:43,900 --> 00:33:45,940
If you refuse me

444
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:50,900
I won't do it because I'm not interested in it at all

445
00:33:53,140 --> 00:33:58,380
Professor Wu, I will do it if you promise me a small request

446
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:03,100
If I win, we both win

447
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:10,940
Ok

448
00:34:12,220 --> 00:34:13,220
I promise you
